# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  FightersEdge AutoStream — local dev environment overrides
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#  This file is for LOCAL DEVELOPMENT ONLY. Copy it to `.env` and tweak.
#
#  None of these values ship to end users. Production builds use the constants
#  defined in src/config.ts. Env vars are only read when the app is running
#  unpackaged (npm run dev, npm run electron:dev) — see setDevMode() calls.
#
#  Therefore: do NOT put production secrets here. There aren't any anyway —
#  the FightersEdge backend is the only thing with credentials, and that's
#  separate.

# ── Backend overrides (point at a local FE backend during dev) ──────────────
# API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:80
# FE_WEB_BASE=http://localhost:8080

# ── Twitch chat-bot OAuth (override the baked-in Client ID for testing) ─────
# TWITCH_CLIENT_ID=your_dev_twitch_client_id

# ── Playlist tuning (override defaults for testing) ─────────────────────────
# QUEUE_SIZE=10
# RECENCY_POOL=20
# RECENCY_DAYS=30
# GAME_IDS=68cba126f261500022897969,67c358569ce15c00218b5873

# ── Local servers ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PLAYER_PORT=3001
